	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can use regular expressions to cut away parts of a debug log that you don't need.  Make sure NTFS compression is enabled for the directory you are making your debug log in.
<br />Except I don't think text editors do too well on 500MB files.  Maybe split it into 50MB files first.
<br />Textpad seems to do better than Notepad++ for these kind of tasks.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
